window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The iconic anthology series of horror tales that's now a feature film!</b></p> <p>Narrated by Patton Oswalt, Melissa McBride, and Alex Brightman, this collection includes all three of Alvin Schwartz's classic story collections: <i>Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark</i>,<i> More Scary Stories to Tell in the Dark</i>, and <i>Scary Stories 3</i>. Walking corpses, dancing bones, knife-wielding madmen, and narrow escapes from death - they're all here in this chilling collection of ghost stories, collected and retold by folklorist Alvin Schwartz. These horrific tales are guaranteed to raise goosebumps. Let the faint of heart beware. </p> <p>Pull up a chair, find a hand to hold, and prepare to be horrified. </p> <p>Supplemental enhancement PDF accompanies the audiobook. </p> <p><b>PLEASE NOTE: When you purchase this title, the accompanying PDF will be available in your Audible Library along with the audio.</b> </p>"; 
